partial_orders.reason: Both edits perform an identical textual substitution pattern: changing 'no_subtitles' to 'no_writesubtitles' in method names. This is a bulk refactoring operation where the same before→after pattern is applied to the same type of syntactic construct (method definitions) across multiple files. Both edits are part of a single, contiguous refactor to rename test methods with a more descriptive name. Either edit can be made first, and after making either, the other becomes a natural next step to complete the uniform renaming pattern.
